track_notes: This route is another which leaves by the footpath at the back of the Patterdale Hotel. St Sunday Crag is our first target then we use a side path avoiding the scramble of Cofa Pike to reach Grisdeal Hause. A steep climb up the side of a broken wall and we reach Seat Sandal. Retreating back to the Hause we tackle an unrelenting climb to Fairfield. Continuing east we turn left at Hart Crag (LDW-027) on a wide ridge via Hartsop above How (LDW-137) to return us to the A592 Kirkstone Pass and the walk back into Patterdale.
track_title: St Sunday Crag - Seat Sandal - Fairfield + 2 Wainwrights

track_notes: Park in the layby, then follow the waterfalls up to the watershed. Turn right to follow the wall to the summit.
